videos.description: Anthony Brown connects with Jeff Smith for a 9-yard touchdown to put the Boston College on the board.
videos.headline: Brown hits Smith for 9-yard Eagles TD

videos.description: Darrell Langham climbs the ladder and gets a foot inbounds for a 13-yard touchdown to the game 7-7.
videos.headline: Langham hauls in 13-yard TD

videos.description: Anthony Brown looks to throw, but finds open space and rushes in for a 5-yard touchdown to give Boston College a 14-7 lead.
videos.headline: Brown runs in a 5-yard TD

videos.description: In the wildcat, DeeJay Dallas takes the direct snap and runs in a 10-yard touchdown to cut the Boston College lead to 17-14.
videos.headline: Dallas rushes in 10-yard TD for Hurricanes

videos.description: The ball pops into the air after Miami's Malik Rosier is sacked and the ball eventually lands in Hamp Cheevers' hands for a Boston College  interception.
videos.headline: Rosier's INT bobbles in the air before Cheevers' INT

videos.description: Malik Rosier is intercepted by Taj_AMit Torres, who sets up Boston College on their onwn 14 yardline.
videos.headline: Boston College collects 2nd interception

videos.description: Up 13 in the fourth quarter, Boston College QB Anthony Brown takes the snap and bursts for a 43-yard run and stays in bounds to keep the clock running.
videos.headline: Brown erupts for a 43-yard run
